  "instructions": [
    "Heat sesame oil in a pan and add garlic paste. Sauté until the garlic paste turns golden brown.",
    "Add turmeric powder, cumin powder, and salt to the pan. Mix well for about 30 seconds.",
    "Fold shrimp into the spice mixture and cook for another minute or until all pieces are coated evenly with spices.",
    "Drizzle butter over the cooked shrimp and mix gently. Serve hot with garnished fresh coriander."
